Reasoning: The paper presents an algorithm based on the functionality of dendritic cells, which is used for anomaly detection. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to artificial intelligence, machine learning, and systems. cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories as they are directly related to artificial intelligence and machine learning. cs.SI and cs.NE are also likely as they are related to systems and neural networks, which could be used in the implementation of the algorithm. Finally, cs.SY is a possible sub-category as it is related to control systems, which could be relevant to the control mechanism for the artificial immune system presented in the paper.
